<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_961434'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_961434'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #18 于:</strong> 2018-11-27, 周二 10:40:39 &#187;</div>
